{
  "number": 91,
  "name": "سُورَةُ الشَّمۡسِ",
  "englishName": "Ash-Shams",
  "englishNameTranslation": "The Sun",
  "revelationType": "Meccan",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 6044,
      "text": "CONSIDER the sun and its radiant brightness,",
      "numberInSurah": 1,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6045,
      "text": "and the moon as it reflects the sun!",
      "numberInSurah": 2,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6046,
      "text": "Consider the day as it reveals the world,",
      "numberInSurah": 3,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6047,
      "text": "and the night as it veils it darkly!",
      "numberInSurah": 4,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6048,
      "text": "Consider the sky and its wondrous make,",
      "numberInSurah": 5,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6049,
      "text": "and the earth and all its expanse!",
      "numberInSurah": 6,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6050,
      "text": "Consider the human self, and how it is formed in accordance with what it is meant to be,",
      "numberInSurah": 7,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6051,
      "text": "and how it is imbued with moral failings as well as with consciousness of God!",
      "numberInSurah": 8,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6052,
      "text": "To a happy state shall indeed attain he who causes this [self] to grow in purity,",
      "numberInSurah": 9,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6053,
      "text": "and truly lost is he who buries it [in darkness].",
      "numberInSurah": 10,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6054,
      "text": "TO [THIS] TRUTH gave the lie, in their overweening arrogance, [the tribe of] Thamud,",
      "numberInSurah": 11,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6055,
      "text": "when that most hapless wretch from among them rushed forward [to commit his evil deed],",
      "numberInSurah": 12,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6056,
      "text": "although God's apostle had told them, \"It is a she-camel belonging to God, so let her drink [and do her no harm]!\"",
      "numberInSurah": 13,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6057,
      "text": "But they gave him the lie, and cruelly slaughtered her - whereupon their Sustainer visited them with utter destruction for this their sin, destroying them all alike:",
      "numberInSurah": 14,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
